The current implementation of [Take operator](https://mxnet.incubator.apache.org/api/python/symbol/symbol.html#mxnet.symbol.take) is incomplete. As mentioned in the documentation, It supports slicing along only axis=0 and in ‘clip’ mode. 

The operator is intended to support other negative and non-negative values for axis. THe current implementation of the operator needs to be modified to meet multiple axis values.

